I want Snow Man
to be everywhere this year.

28
00:02:17,804 --> 00:02:19,272
I hope we can be in an anime.

29
00:02:19,339 --> 00:02:21,741
<i>The boys have closely bonded
with one another.</i>

30
00:02:24,911 --> 00:02:27,514
<i>Even when a junior group beat them
to make their debut,</i>

31
00:02:27,580 --> 00:02:30,683
<i>they weren't discouraged
and kept aiming for greater heights.</i>

32
00:02:32,018 --> 00:02:34,220
{\an8}I want to overcome being unknown.

33
00:02:34,521 --> 00:02:36,489
{\an8}I want people to know who we are.

34
