35
00:02:41,227 --> 00:02:43,229
{\an8}<i>Kyoto's Minamiza Theatre.</i>

36
00:02:48,134 --> 00:02:50,503
<i>Just what kind of show will they create?</i>

37
00:02:56,276 --> 00:02:58,278
<i>The days before the show's completion</i>

38
