{\an8}3 NEW MEMBERS TURN 6 TO 9

49
00:03:39,652 --> 00:03:42,121
You've shaken your nerves loose
quickly, Raul.

50
00:03:42,188 --> 00:03:44,123
That's for the best, definitely!

51
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,592
I'm just pretending.

52
00:03:46,993 --> 00:03:50,697
<i>The first is a 15-year-old
